\newlabel{tab:oracle-portability}{{4}{9}{Supplementary 200-item canonicalized OBIMD$\rightarrow $EVOBC portability probe. The multitask model is read through its \texttt {<literal>} field, and a simple open 2-way selector lifts the dictionary-grounded prompt from 40/200 to 44/200 exact matches while reducing contamination from 3.5\% to 0.5\%}{table.4}{}}
